Note: ================================================================
Note: Parser Tests
Note: ================================================================

Process called "test_parser_document_structure" that takes suite_ptr as Integer returns Integer:
    Let source be "\\documentclass{article}\\begin{document}Hello\\end{document}"
    Let lexer_ptr be proc create_lexer from LaTeXLexer with source
    proc tokenize from LaTeXLexer with lexer_ptr

    Let tokens be proc get_tokens from LaTeXLexer with lexer_ptr
    Let parser_ptr be proc create_parser from LaTeXParser with tokens
    Let ast be proc parse from LaTeXParser with parser_ptr

    proc assert_true from suite_ptr, "Parser creates AST", ast is not equal to 0

    Let node_type be proc read_integer from Memory at ast with 0
    proc assert_true from suite_ptr, "AST root is DOCUMENT node", node_type is equal to LaTeXParser.NODE_DOCUMENT

    Return 1
End Process

Process called "test_parser_preamble" that takes suite_ptr as Integer returns Integer:
    Let source be "\\documentclass[12pt]{article}\\usepackage{amsmath}"
