    proc assert_true from suite_ptr, "HIR node is MATH_INLINE type", node_type is equal to LaTeXToHIR.HIR_LATEX_MATH_INLINE

    Return 1
End Process

Process called "test_translate_environments" that takes suite_ptr as Integer returns Integer:
