Process called "test_roundtrip_simple_document" that takes suite_ptr as Integer returns Integer:
    Let source be "\\documentclass{article}\\begin{document}Hello World\\end{document}"
    Let result be proc latex_roundtrip from LaTeXEmitter with source

    proc assert_true from suite_ptr, "Round-trip produces output", proc string_length from StringCore with result is greater than 0

    Note: Check that result contains key elements
    Let contains_documentclass be proc string_contains from StringCore with result, "\\documentclass"
    proc assert_true from suite_ptr, "Round-trip preserves documentclass", contains_documentclass is equal to 1

    Return 1
End Process

