Note: ================================================================
Note: Validation Tests
Note: ================================================================

Process called "test_validate_valid_document" that takes suite_ptr as Integer returns Integer:
    Let source be "\\documentclass{article}\\begin{document}Valid\\end{document}"
    Let is_valid be proc validate_latex from LaTeXEmitter with source

    proc assert_true from suite_ptr, "Valid document passes validation", is_valid is equal to 1

    Return 1
End Process

Process called "test_validate_invalid_document" that takes suite_ptr as Integer returns Integer:
    Let source be "\\invalid{missing braces"
    Let is_valid be proc validate_latex from LaTeXEmitter with source

    proc assert_true from suite_ptr, "Invalid document fails validation", is_valid is equal to 0

    Return 1
End Process

